1
00:00:39,840 --> 00:00:41,520
Why doesn't she picking up the phone?

2
00:00:52,740 --> 00:00:56,216
Ranya, you need to go up there and speak instead of your sister now.

3
00:00:58,140 --> 00:01:00,208
No. I’m not going up.

4
00:01:01,264 --> 00:01:03,264
You have to. Go, right now!

5
00:01:32,270 --> 00:01:33,016
P'Chat!

6
00:01:34,820 --> 00:01:36,400
P'Chat, what’s wrong?

7
00:01:37,368 --> 00:01:37,928
P'Chat!

8
00:01:37,960 --> 00:01:39,968
I’m okay... Ranya, help me up.

9
00:01:40,128 --> 00:01:42,256
P'Chat, what happened to you?

10
00:02:11,020 --> 00:02:13,368
Hm... where did Pimchat go?

11
00:02:14,010 --> 00:02:17,368
She’s the Vice President, but she’s showing zero responsibility.

12
00:02:18,510 --> 00:02:20,728
I agree. It’s unacceptable.

13
00:02:21,340 --> 00:02:23,920
By the way... where is Ranya?

14
00:02:25,110 --> 00:02:27,664
She went to follow her sister,

15
00:02:27,688 --> 00:02:29,660
of course she is a good girl.

16
00:02:32,140 --> 00:02:35,280
I’ll just go up instead.

17
00:02:35,500 --> 00:02:36,192
Please, after you.

18
00:02:37,144 --> 00:02:38,288
Wait!

19
00:03:05,672 --> 00:03:06,912
I’m here.

20
00:03:36,910 --> 00:03:39,952
I would like to thank all our distinguished guests

21
00:03:40,208 --> 00:03:44,080
for honoring us with your presence at the launch of our group's new project.

22
00:03:49,290 --> 00:03:54,504
Even though my father is no longer with us, under my management,

23
00:03:55,170 --> 00:03:59,984
I promise to take our company as far as I possibly can.

24
00:04:32,130 --> 00:04:33,416
Walk slowly.

25
00:04:33,970 --> 00:04:35,104
Be careful...

26
00:04:35,940 --> 00:04:37,272
watch your step.

27
00:04:38,310 --> 00:04:39,312
Are you okay?

28
00:04:40,984 --> 00:04:42,912
Thank you for coming to help me.

29
00:04:45,130 --> 00:04:46,544
I’m always happy to.

30
00:04:47,120 --> 00:04:50,256
Like I told you, I’ll always be by your side.

31
00:05:00,980 --> 00:05:03,360
Wait... P’Chat, what are you doing?

32
00:05:05,480 --> 00:05:07,072
We’re siblings.

33
00:05:18,300 --> 00:05:19,576
What is... this?

34
00:05:20,330 --> 00:05:21,728
Try opening it, Ran.

35
00:05:27,780 --> 00:05:30,032
Your mother faked the DNA results.

36
00:05:30,470 --> 00:05:32,208
I just received the real ones myself.

37
00:05:33,480 --> 00:05:37,664
So... we aren’t siblings?

38
00:05:39,248 --> 00:05:41,008
We aren’t siblings.

39
00:05:44,050 --> 00:05:45,904
I’m not K’Wichai’s daughter?

40
00:05:46,740 --> 00:05:51,528
Then... P’Chat, I...

41
00:05:55,510 --> 00:05:57,296
Can I beg you?

42
00:05:58,340 --> 00:06:00,136
I need to go talk to my mother first.

43
00:06:01,020 --> 00:06:03,072
Please don't do anything yet.

44
00:06:08,400 --> 00:06:10,480
If you want to talk to her,

45
00:06:10,750 --> 00:06:14,008
to get her to back down quietly then I won't do anything.

46
00:06:16,800 --> 00:06:18,640
I don’t want my mother to go to jail.

47
00:06:20,860 --> 00:06:22,736
Go talk to her first.

48
00:06:24,560 --> 00:06:25,584
I’ll wait.

49
00:06:29,480 --> 00:06:30,776
Thank you.

50
00:06:38,970 --> 00:06:44,392
Can I have something else instead of a "thank you"?

51
00:06:46,870 --> 00:06:48,472
I’ve missed you so much.

52
00:06:52,820 --> 00:06:53,936
I want to hold you,

53
00:06:57,520 --> 00:06:58,928
kiss your cheek,

54
00:07:04,620 --> 00:07:05,624
and really kiss you.
